TextEng: Hello Oleff. I am <FullName>. Will you answer some questions?
Text: 안녕하세요, 올레프. 저는 <FullName>입니다. 몇 가지 질문에 답해 주시겠습니까?

TextEng: My name is <FirstName>. I have some questions for you.
Text: 제 이름은 <FirstName>입니다. 몇 가지 질문이 있습니다.

TextEng: I'm <FirstName>. Enough chatter. I have questions for you.
Text: 난 <FirstName> 입니다. 잡담은 그만하고. 질문이 있습니다.

TextEng: Me <FullName>. Maybe me ask some questions?
Me <FirstName>. Stop yappin' and answer questions, okay?
Text: 나 <FirstName>. 수다 그만하고 질문에 답해, 알겠지?

TextEng: Farewell for now.
Bye bye then.
What is your position here?
What your job here?
What are the tenets of the Tyrran faith?
What stuff do Tyrrans believe?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> That might sound harsh to some people.
Me needs temple stuff. What you gots?
I require temple services. What can you offer?
Text: 사원에서 제공하는 서비스가 필요합니다. 무엇을 이용할 수 있죠?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Maybe me can still help?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 아직 나도 도울 수 있지 않을까?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I might still be able to help.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 혹시 도움이 될 수 있을지도 모릅니다.

TextEng: The plague undoubtedly complicated things.
Text: 역병 때문에 일이 틀어진 건 분명하군요.

TextEng: Plague probably loused things up good.
Your efforts were likely wasted when the plague hit.
Text: 역병이 덮치며 당신들의 노력이 물거품이 되었겠군요.

TextEng: All you did probably useless when plague happen.
Text: 역병 나고 나선 네가 한 거 다 소용없었겠지.

TextEng: A waste of time, even before the plague hit.
Text: 역병이 오기 전부터 애초에 시간 낭비였던 거죠.

TextEng: Bah! Diggin' is stupid, even before plague hit.
I will help you find these tombs.
Me help find tombs and dead guys.
Text: 나 무덤이랑 죽은 사람들 찾는 거 도와줄게.

TextEng: I have no interest in helping.
Me no want to bother with this.
What do you know about Halueth Never?
Who this Halueth Never guy?
No! Me demands more!
Give me a copy of your letter.
Me needs copy of yous letter thing.
Me not care about this.
Farewell for now.
Bye bye
Go over what is needed again.
Text: 필요한 것을 다시 한번 정리해 주십시오.

TextEng: You repeat stuff about this job, okay?
Text: 이 일 다시 설명해 줘, 응?

TextEng: Farewell for now.
Bye bye for now.
Yeah yeah, I'll look into it sometime.
Me get around to it maybe later.
Go over the task with me. Perhaps I will help too.
Text: 의뢰 내용을 다시 설명해 주세요. 나도 도울지 모르니까요.

TextEng: You tell me stuff too. Maybe me help.
Text: 너도 얘기해 봐. 나도 도울지 몰라.

TextEng: This doesn't interest me. Farewell.
Me not care much. Bye.
Me gots stuff from one of the tomb-things.
Text: 나 무덤 중 하나에서 물건 가져왔어.

TextEng: I have an artifact from one of the tombs.
I have a copy of your letter and will look into it.
Me gots a letter from you. Me look into tomb stuff.
Text: 나 너한테서 편지 받았어. 나 무덤 조사할게.

TextEng: I have no interest in this.
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of the Ancient Chronicles of Never.</Start>
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of Halueth Never's rusted armor.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>할루스 네버의 녹슨 갑옷 회수에 대해 설명합니다.</Start>

TextEng: Nevermind.
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of the ancient Holy Symbol of Tyr.</Start>
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You must agree that I am worth more.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 제 값어치가 더 하다는 데 동의하시겠죠.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You knows me worth more than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 그보다 값어치 더 있는 거 알잖아.

TextEng: I demand more, lest you need a tomb of your own!
Text: 더 내놓으시오, 안 그러면 당신도 묘자리를 쓰게 될 겁니다!

TextEng: Me wants more, or me put you in tomb like Never!
Text: 더 줘, 아니면 너도 네버처럼 무덤에 넣어 버릴 거야!

TextEng: Me come back if find more, okay.
That is sufficient. Thank you.
That really good. Thanks for the stuff.
I shall return if I find more.
That will not do! I demand more!
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of Jacob's blessed quill from the evil Gilles.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>사악한 길레스에게서 제이콥의 축복받은 깃펜 회수에 대해 설명합니다.</Start>

TextEng: <StartAction>Describe the recovery of Jacob's blessed quill from the evil Gilles.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>사악한 길레스에게서 제이콥의 축복받은 깃펜 회수에 대해 설명합니다.</Start>

TextEng: Farewell
Bye bye
I have a letter from Ophala for you.
Me gots letter from Ophala for yous.
Text: 나 오팔라가 너한테 보내는 편지 있어.

TextEng: Why do you consort with a sinful operation?
Me thought you good. Why you work with dirty people?
Text: 나 너 선하다고 생각했어. 왜 더러운 사람들이랑 일해?

TextEng: Gold. I want gold to keep quiet about you.
Text: 금화요. 당신 일을 입 다물려면 금화가 필요합니다.

TextEng: Me wants gold to shut up. Heh.
Text: 입 다물어 줄게. 금화나 내놔. 헤헷.

TextEng: Yes, you will pay me now.
Yeah! You pay me good!
<StartAction>Describe the recovery of Jacob's blessed quill from the evil Gilles.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>사악한 길레스에게서 제이콥의 축복받은 깃펜 회수에 대해 설명합니다.</Start>

TextEng: Me needs temple stuffs.
I require temple services.
Me needs temple stuff.
I need temple services.
Me need temple stuff.
I need temple services.
I think I've found a Tyrran artifact. Does it interest you?
Text: 티르의 유물을 찾은 것 같아요. 관심 있어요?

TextEng: Me found Tyr old thingy in tomb. You interested in it?
Text: 나 무덤에서 티르 옛날 물건 찾았어. 너 관심 있어?
